reviewText: I seen this movie years ago and loved it. Its nice to see a movie with a plot. Its about this girl who inherits her uncles boat however there is a loan out against it for 40000. So Carrie and her 2 friends Tracy, Ashley have to pay 10000 per month for 4 months to a shady loan officer (who wants the boat himself). There are 4 parts to this movie and this is the final episode.
